                  </div>
                  <div class="container__title">
                    <h3>2. Together we discuss it</h3>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container__desc">
                  <p>Let us get acquainted and discuss all the possible variants and options. Google hangouts or Skype usually works great.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="container__item">
                <div class="container__top">
                  <div class="container__circle">
                  </div>
                  <div class="container__title">
                    <h3>3. Let's start building</h3>
                  </div>
                </div>
